@20649 = ~This magical tome affects a single reader.  It takes one full week of uninterrupted study to read and comprehend.  The reader gains the permanent, inherent spell-like ability of freedom of movement.  This ability is lost forever if the character should ever cause the death of a rose plant, even inadvertently.

