@20697 = ~After defeating the bandit leader, Rolf Sureblade in his fortification north of Soubar, you recovered this shield of awesome defense.  This shield is truly an item that you should treasure, as it is bound to save your life more than once as you adventure throughout Faerűn.  This shield decreases AC by 6 and adds 3 to all saving throws.  In addition, Sureblade's shield allows the you to move so quickly that your movement rate is increased by 2 and normal missiles have no chance of striking him. 

