@20699 = ~After defeating the bandit leader, Rolf Sureblade in his fortification north of Soubar, you recovered this sword of great power that he wielded against you in that horrific battle for your life.  This sword is truly a weapon worthy of your skills, as it allows you to cut through the defenses of most other creatures.  Upon a successful hit against a target of 18th level of less, the creature is instantly killed when struck, an ability which can be quite useful when forced to fight powerful enemies.

