@20704 = ~This is one of many pipes that perform the same function:  that of leading rats to wherever the pipe player plays this flute.  Upon blowing the flute normally, the strangly hypnotic music will draw regular rats from the surrounding areas as they become pleasantly soothed by the music.  This can be a blessing for some, a curse to others as the rats will of course mob an area where the pipe is played.

STATISTICS:

